      "text": [
        "3628 - وَ قَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"مِنْ سَعَادَةِ اَلْمَرْءِ أَنْ يَكُونَ اَلْقَيِّمَ عَلَى عِيَالِهِ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3628 - Imam (as) said: \"Part of a man's happiness is that he is the caretaker of his family.\""
        ]
